om/\">RhodeCode</a>: Centralized control for distributed repositories. Mercurial, Git, and Subversion under a single roof.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Be-Organized</h2><h3>GTD-Task Manager</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://todo.microsoft.com/tasks\">Microsoft To Do</a> (<code>Cloud</code>,<code>Mac</code>,<code>Win</code>,<code>Android</code>,<code>iOS</code>,<code>Win Store</code>,<code>Chrome OS</code>): Almost perfect todo lists with cooperation and sharing.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Be-Organized</h2><h3>GTD-Task Manager</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://keep.google.com/\">Google Keep</a>(<code>Cloud</code>,<code>Android</code>,<code>iOS</code>,<code>Chrome OS</code>)</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Be-Organized</h2><h3>GTD-Task Manager</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://agenda.com/\">Agenda</a>(<code>Mac</code>): Date-focused note taking.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Cloud Services</h2><h3>Math and Programming Online</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://colab.research.google.com/\">Google Colab</a>: free jupyter notebook online. Google Colab also comes with free GPU hours.\n<ul>\n<li>Free and powerful.</li>\n<li>Share and collaborate on the same notebook.</li>\n<li>Can be saved in GitHub or Google Drive.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Cloud Services</h2><h3>Math and Programming Online</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://nextjournal.com/\">NextJournal</a>: the notebook for reproducible research.\n<ul>\n<li>Basically, NextJournal runs almost anything.</li>\n<li>Focusing on reproducibility.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Cloud Services</h2><h3>Math and Programming Online</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.kaggle.com/\">Kaggle</a>: kaggle has built-in free jupyter notebook.\n<ul>\n<li>One can also connect to Google BigQuery to access big data.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Cloud Services</h2><h3>Math and Programming Online</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://notebooks.azure.com/\">Azure Notebooks</a>: online jupyter notebooks.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Cloud Services</h2><h3>Math and Programming Online</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://datalore.io/\">Datalore</a>: online jupyter notebook by JetBrains.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Cloud Services</h2><h3>Math and Programming Online</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/sagemaker/\">SageMaker</a>: AWS service with a lot of tools integrated. Sagemaker comes with the Sagemake Studio which provides jupyter notebook for programmer and other charting and data management tools.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Cloud Services</h2><h3>Math and Programming Online</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.wolfram.com/mathematica/online/\">Mathematica Online</a>: Bring Mathematica to life in the cloud.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Cloud Services</h2><h3>Plotting and Charting Online</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.geogebra.org\">GeoGebra</a>: very old but still very good. GeoGebra can be used for precise charting as well as calculations.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Publishing and Sharing</h2><h3>Hosting</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/\">AWS</a>: Amazon AWS provide student perks.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Publishing and Sharing</h2><h3>Blog and CMS</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.gitbook.com/\">GitBook</a> (<code>Cloud</code>): write in Markdown and collaborate with the team. GitBook integrates with GitHub so no content will be lost.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Publishing and Sharing</h2><h3>Blog and CMS</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/\">Wordpress</a> (<code>PHP</code>): Very popular but requires a lot of maintenance.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Note Taking</h2><h3>Notebooks for Researchers</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://findingsapp.com\">Findings</a>: Your research assistant &#x26; lab notebook, all in one app.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Note Taking</h2><h4>Markdown</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://stackedit.io/\">StackEdit</a>(<code>Cloud</code>): StackEdit is a Markdown editor with many integrated services such as math (MathJax), Google Drive, Dropbox, and GitHub.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Presentation Tools</h2><h3>Online Load and Edit</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.slideas.app/\">Slideas</a>: the easiest way to create a beautiful Markdown Presentation, with all the features you need.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Presentation Tools</h2><h3>Mathematica</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://reference.wolfram.com/language/howto/CreateASlideShow.html\">Mathematica slides</a> can be made interactive.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Programming</h2><h3>Code Editors</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/\">Visual Studio Code, aka VS Code</a>(<code>Free</code>,<code>Cross-platform</code>,<code>Plugins</code>): same technology as atom but faster than atom, and Microsoft made.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Programming</h2><h3>Coding is Fun</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://codefights.com/\">Code Fights</a></li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>Data Visualization and Graph Making</h2><h3>Data Visualization</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://d3js.org/\">D3 js</a> (<code>js</code>)</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"emptymalei/awesome-research","categoryHTML":"<h2>MISC</h2><h3>More</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://unpaywall.org/\">Unpay Wall</a>: legally download research papers for free.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-12-07T12:21:30.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"tokenmill/awesome-nlg","categoryHTML":"<h2>Neural Natural Language Generation</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/minimaxir/textgenrnn\">textgenrnn</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/minimaxir/textgenrnn\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007